h4 Multi-step
p.-text
  | For multi-step modals, ensure the class <code>-centered</code> is applied
  | to <code>a-modal__title</code>. This will provide sufficient real estate on the
  | left side to store a back button <code>a-modal__back</code>.
.example.-mb3
  .a-modal__backdrop.-p6(style="position:relative;border-top-left-radius:3px;border-top-right-radius:3px;")
    .a-modal(style="margin-top:0;")
      .a-modal__header
